## Part 2: GoPlausible Bazaar (x402 Service Discovery)

### How It Works

GoPlausible Bazaar is the service registry for x402-enabled APIs. AI agents discover your API here and pay automatically.

### What Was Wired

New function [registerWithBazaar()](file:///d:/Hackathons/Algoplay/algopay/src/x402/bazaar.ts#74-147) in [src/x402/bazaar.ts](file:///d:/Hackathons/Algoplay/algopay/src/x402/bazaar.ts):
- POSTs to `https://api.goplausible.xyz/discovery/resources`
- Sends: name, description, serviceUrl, priceUsdc, payToAddress, network, tags
- Falls back gracefully if offline (non-fatal)

New CLI command: `algopay x402 bazaar register`

### Get a Bazaar API Key

1. Go to [https://goplausible.xyz](https://goplausible.xyz)
2. Sign up / sign in
3. Generate an API key from your dashboard
4. Add to `.env`:

```env
BAZAAR_API_KEY=your_key_here
```

### Register Your Endpoint

```bash
# First ensure you're authenticated
algopay auth login your@email.com
algopay auth verify <flowId> <otp>

# Then register your API
algopay x402 bazaar register https://your-api.example.com/v1/data \
  --name "My Weather API" \
  --price 0.05 \
  --description "Real-time weather data — pay per request" \
  --category data \
  --tags "weather,data,real-time"
```

**JSON output:**
```bash
algopay x402 bazaar register https://... --name "..." --price 0.05 --json
```

### Verify Registration

```bash
algopay x402 bazaar search "weather"
# Should now find your listing
```

---

## Full `.env` Reference

```env
# ── Server ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=3001
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-random-32-char-string

# ── Email (OTP delivery) ────────────────────────────────────────
SENDGRID_API_KEY=SG.xxxxxx   # leave empty → OTP printed to console (dev)
ALGOPAY_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com

# ── Storage ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379   # leave empty → in-memory fallback

# ── Intermezzo (Wallet KMS) ─────────────────────────────────────
INTERMEZZO_URL=http://localhost:3000   # leave empty → mock mode (valid algosdk addr)
INTERMEZZO_TOKEN=your_pawn_jwt_here

# ── Algorand Network ─────────────────────────────────────────────
ALGOD_URL=https://testnet-api.algonode.cloud
INDEXER_URL=https://testnet-idx.algonode.cloud

# ── GoPlausible Bazaar ───────────────────────────────────────────
BAZAAR_API_KEY=your_bazaar_key_here   # leave empty → registration skipped
```

---

## End-to-End Flow After Integration

```
User                CLI / Server           Intermezzo           Algorand
  │                      │                     │                    │
  ├─ auth login ─────────►                     │                    │
  │             (OTP sent via SendGrid)         │                    │
  ├─ auth verify ─────────►                    │                    │
  │                      ├─ createAccount ─────►                    │
  │                      │◄── {address} ───────┘                    │
  │◄── {sessionToken, walletAddress} ──────────────────────────────┤
  │                                                                  │
  ├─ fund --watch ──────►                                           │
  │                      ├─── Indexer poll for USDC deposits ───────►
  │◄── deposit list ─────┤◄──────────────────────────────────────── │
  │                                                                  │
  ├─ x402 pay <url> ────►                                           │
  │                      ├─── signTransactions ─────► Intermezzo   │
  │                      │◄── signed txns ───────────┘             │
  │                      ├─── broadcast tx ─────────────────────── ►
  │◄── {txId, response} ─┤                                          │
```
